<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Harvest Mechanism 19:11-A</h3>

    <p>A multitude of pipes extend into the red ocean, pumping continuous fire into a mechanical tower adorned with various meters and dials. At the base of the tower, a network of even more pipes sprawl in various directions across the sulfur shore.</p>

    <p>An <button type="button" class="whiteMarker goldSphere" board="65">gold sphere</button> hovers over the red surf.</p>

    <p>You can go <a class="panelOpener" identifier="east">ea�s��</a>, where you glimpse more towers, or back [[west|moltenPumps]].</p>
</div>
</snippet>


<snippet name="brimstoneFields" tags="fire">

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Brimstone Fields</h3>

    <p>Occasional arcs of flame play upon hissing sulfur. The temperature is burning hot. Barriers of flame shoot up from the smoking fields, preventing passage in any direction except [[north|moltenPumps]] and [[south|moltenPumpsSouth]].</p>
</div>
</snippet>

<snippet name="moltenPumpsSouth" tags="fire">

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Molten Pumps - South</h3>

    <p>You find an ocean of fire identical to the first, but facing south instead of north. Enormous rusted machines stand all around you, their pumps sluggish but still quite operational. Molten puddles of a glowing red-gold substance cover the ground. The <button type="button" class="whiteMarker goldSphere" board="66">gold sphere</button> floats above one such puddle.</p>

    <p>You can only go [[north|brimstoneFields]]; bulwarks of rusted machinery block any other path.</p>
</div>
</snippet>

